Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一直在殺她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永無止境地追殺她 無數次 無數次 無數次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說妳已經習慣了殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會不斷侵蝕妳的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是只有我才能做得到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 真那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰中止 回收至世界之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.20,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(528.344,435)}Fraxinus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 你聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 你在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續約會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我黃豆麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭克福麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小籠包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香 我手頭沒有錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 令音把魔法卡片借給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這不是白吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令音告訴了我 狂三和真那的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須阻止狂三像這樣無止境地殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我卻沒有自信面對這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三雖然是精靈 但是和十香和四糸乃迥異
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事喔 士道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三和我沒有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有士道陪伴著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是士道拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天這樣士道邀請我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我展現了這個世界溫暖的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:06:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有士道 我可能會變得和現在的狂三一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說我和狂三有不同的話 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊有沒有人伸出援助之手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 十香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了妳讓我明白了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 士道就由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓我受到鼓舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 能讓此刻多停留一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同學 你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五河士道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛到學校就這麼囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法直視
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 現在能別打擾士道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法直視
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為士道同學今天肯定是要請假的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定拯救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了很奇怪的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不讓妳殺人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不讓真那殺妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同學 就讓我來試驗一下你說的話究竟是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塔托斯克機關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.21,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ratatoskr
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到妳和哥哥在那種組織裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧妳調查了這麼多呢 目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五河士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓赤手空拳的哥哥去和精靈會面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經失去作為妹妹的資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的事情 就由我來接手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 想叫我把士道託付給DEM社這樣的惡德企業嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:35.54,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(677.531,435)}Deus ex machina
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼知道這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太小瞧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了拉塔托斯克以外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.04,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ratatoskr
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供給顯現裝置給世界上的軍隊和警察的軍事企業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是從那裡來到AST的公司職員對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未能確認時崎狂三是否下課了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是 她有沒有偷聽到我們的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 琴里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就由我來做領航員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上進行解析
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我們是惡德企業 我可不能置若罔聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡給予了失去記憶的我以存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個讓我感激不盡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是認真的？居然被弄到那種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對崇宮真那用過的杯子內所提取到的體液進行了一番調查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的全身被施加了大量的魔力處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計只能活不到十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 來禪高中內出現了強烈的靈波反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是時崎狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣域結界 是使範圍內的人類變得衰弱的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三她為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是覺得身體實在太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時封印十香和四糸乃的靈力於體內的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像受到了精靈的加護一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種狀況下 能夠正常活動的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同學 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找我有事的話 就請到屋頂上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請儘快來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十香 妳在這裡休息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我會去拯救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,識別 AST 鳶一折紙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基礎顯現裝置 啟動承認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 等你很久了 士道同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳使用了緊急著裝吧 狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常危險 請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折紙同學 這麼著急是要去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時崎狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 此路不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 士道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一個人去 士道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體動起來 動起來 動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好啊 十香同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 妳做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧 蝕時之城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦踏上我的影子就會被吸取時間的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間？那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的時間 也就是壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天使擁有驚人的力量 但是相應地要消耗大量的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此時不時地 需要從外部進行充能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人不幸都是我可愛的餌料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只有士道是與眾不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我為了與你合為一體  為了直接吃掉你才來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是妳的目標的話 沒必要做那麼過分的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃掉你之前 我想讓你收回今天早上的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拯救我之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道同學 就因為這個理由而做這些事的我是不是很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可恨吧 明白了我是不值得憐憫的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所 以 說 請把那句話收回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣做的話 讓我把這個結界解開也是可以的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對 快點嘛 要是錯過時機的話可就無法挽回了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳解開結界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 收回那句話我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我厭煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白這個聲音代表著什麼意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間震警報？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非時崎狂三她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自發地引起作為突發災害的空間震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不打算收回那句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果空間震發生了的話 失去知覺的學生們會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小士 狂三的精神狀態正在發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很有可能會襲擊你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 狂三 妳說過妳的目的是吃掉我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓空間震停下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就從這裡跳下去自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己當人質？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是幼稚的想法 你要是敢跳就跳一個我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明我有作為人質的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請妳停下空間震嗎 另外把這結界也解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我咬舌自盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有要求?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 妳還能再一次重來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還執著於那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也許會喜歡上那種理所應當的和平生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則妳也不會這麼享受和我的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 我能讓妳做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的罪孽需要用一生去償還
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是狂三 無論妳錯得多深 都無法動搖我要拯救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 我 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的喔 被花言巧語迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 我明白了 請安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候的我可能太年輕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不要再兜圈子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 又是千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都這麼厲害 真不愧是真那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼輕易地劈開我的靈裝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還不能這麼輕易地被妳殺掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻刻帝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.83,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Zaphkiel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四之彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:24.92,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dalet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人瞠目的恢復能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喔 是讓時間倒流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧來吧 讓我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意 我會一如既往地殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是絕對無法殺掉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從妳喉嚨開始割裂妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aleph
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七之彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.82,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zayin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 大家都到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂三 竟然在戰鬥中逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓妳跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 人家好怕怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我一個弱女子 竟然這麼多人欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 今天我是動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs(28)}怎麼樣 開心吧 一起來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的過去 我的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各個時間軸上的我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 殺不盡我的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我們一起完結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 為了讓你無法再蠱惑我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得將絕望銘刻到你心中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可真的會有好多人死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間震發生時如果遇到同樣規模的震動 會被抵消
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士道 把它稍微還給我下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦灼吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼爛殲鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.47,yinzhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Camael
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始我們的戰爭吧
